                     <interp inst="t18510707-1528-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18510707-1528-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>, <hi rend="italic">Jun</hi>., stealing 1 pair of shoes, 2 spoons, 8 knives, and other articles, value 5<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 16<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18510707-name-511" type="victimName">
